description:
The &#8216;Billie&#8217; bag is a vision in miniature.She is perfect for those minimalist days, when you can pack light and leave your worries behind.

	Upcycled from a 100% pure wool kilt, she is beautifully soft and squishy, and eco-friendly all at once!. Her handle and flap are made from a cobat blue and black houndstooth twill in a wool blend, and she is lined with a fab red floral cotton. At the back, she has a functional patch pocket. Embellished and fastened with some beautiful vintage fabric-covered buttons from my button box, she is a real cutie!

	Bright, kitsch and fabulously scottish, she is a must have!

	Measurements:
Length: 27cm/ 10.5&#8221; 
Width: 29cm/ 11.5&#8221; 
Handles: 122cm/ 50&#8221; 
Width at opening: 20cm/ 8&#8221;

	Surface clean only.
First two photos courtesy of <span class="caps">EMD</span> photography.

Kathryn is a sophisticated little minx, perfect for those long leisured days shopping in the city. Spacious enough for all your wordly needs, this oversized look is bang on trend right now, but the gorgeous tweed keeps it classic looking too. It would also be an ideal overnight bag.

	Upcycled from a pleated tweed skirt, the shape of this bag retains the character of the skirt and is even lined with the original skirt lining! Eco-chic!

	The bag is 100% wool, with a cotton twill top band and acetate lining. The handles are stitched securely, and strengthed with the addition of a button at the base. The bag is then embellished with one of our signature corsages.

	Measuremnts
Width at base: 44cm/ 17.5&#8221; 
Width at opening: 27cm/ 10.5&#8221; 
Length: 40cm/ 15.5&#8221; 
Handles: 80cm/ 31&#8221;

	Surface clean only.

	First two photos courtesy of <span class="caps">EMD</span> photography.
